snippet.title: Tokyo Ghoul:re 「katharsis」- Season 2 Op (Metal Cover)
snippet.description:
As I said before, I came back with a new Tokyo Ghoul cover song. With my proud Friedrich and guitarist 'Wee' and a new guest, Ollie, we have infused new life of this song with different interpretation. I personally super satisfied with the result, I hope you enjoy it too and let me know what you think!

►Spotify
https://goo.gl/qvFA3h

►Soundcloud
https://goo.gl/kQhDJR

►Google Play
https://goo.gl/2a1UXH

►iTunes
https://goo.gl/YwjD5U

Tokyo Ghoul:re | 東京喰種:re 「katharsis」 (Ultimate Metal Cover) - Season 2 Op Full Version

Siegfried Song (Symmetric Chaos, South Korea) - Lead Vocals, Harmony Vocals, Video Editing
'WEE' SungHun (MuTrickster, South Korea) - Rhythm and Lead Guitars
Friedrich Habetler (FH Music, Austria) - Producing, Mixing, Mastering
Ollie Bernstein (Illusion Force, USA) - Bass Guitars
